    <title>Parameters</title>

    <section id="suffix">
	<title><varname>suffix</varname> (string)</title>
	<para>
	    The suffix to be appended to the end of the header field. You can
	    use the parameter to specify additional parameters to be added to
	    the header field, see the example.
	</para>
	<para>
	    Default value is "" (empty string).
	</para>
	<example>
	    <title><varname>suffix</varname> usage</title>
	    <programlisting>
modparam("diversion", "suffix", ";privacy=full")
</programlisting>
	    </example>
    </section>

